{"tid":773896,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[[連登最愛]]  非竄改！Mazda和Suzuki針對油耗/排放造假醜聞正式道歉","createTime":"2018-08-10T01:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T09:39:33.000Z","uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea80d0b9e2472c5308d619b6c198a5ce879eaf5","tid":773896,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:47:11.000Z","msg":"概覽：<br />\nMazda和Suzuki於昨日稍晚，正式舉行記者會，坦承新車於測試上的確有所疏失，但絕無惡意竄改數據！<br />\n<br />\n這回捲入車輛油耗/排放造假醜聞的除了Mazda和Suzuki，尚有Yamaha，三家車廠也正式於8/9下午舉行記者會向大眾道歉，據日本國土交通省公布的調查結果， Mazda抽樣1875輛，有72輛數據有問題；Suzuki的12819抽樣中查出6401輛； Yamaha的335輛抽樣中則有7輛有問題，其中Suzuki出現瑕疵的比例高達49.9％（Mazda為3.8％、Yamaha為2.1％）！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過Mazda和Suzuki都表示，出現問題的車輛都並非人為的惡意竄改數據，而是在測試過程中的瑕疵所造成，之後也會在程序上更加嚴謹，並加強人員訓練，防止次類狀況再發生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photo.8891.com.tw/nc/newcar/article/2018/08/10/1533863417309365_720_720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphoto.8891.com.tw%2Fnc%2Fnewcar%2Farticle%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F1533863417309365_720_720.jpg&h=be32fd98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photo.8891.com.tw/nc/newcar/article/2018/08/10/1533863418844153_720_720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphoto.8891.com.tw%2Fnc%2Fnewcar%2Farticle%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F1533863418844153_720_720.jpg&h=405d4cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photo.8891.com.tw/nc/newcar/article/2018/08/10/1533863419588038_720_720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphoto.8891.com.tw%2Fnc%2Fnewcar%2Farticle%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F1533863419588038_720_720.jpg&h=dee6a183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b82670f7681a11de66bd59fc3890a4ba84219305","tid":773896,"uid":190601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T02:07:40.000Z","msg":"Toyota 徹完資先公布，真識食"},{"pid":"04dc2329d5f4be2bdff320307edd23cb023f447c","tid":773896,"uid":40880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:39:42.000Z","msg":"有